<P ID="CN026683.EP2V77"><PB N="26" REF="26">VER. 77.
<HI>What has not fir'd etc.</HI>] in the MS.<Q><L>In who&s;e mad brain the mixt ideas roll</L>
<L>Of Tall-boy's breeches, and of Cae&s;ar's &s;oul.</L></Q></P>
<P ID="CN026683.EP2V122"><PB N="28" REF="28">After ver. 122. in the MS.
<Q><L>Oppre&s;s'd with wealth and wit, abundance &s;ad!</L>
