<L>In&s;tead of Berenice to think on Be&s;s.</L>
<L>Thus while immortal Cibber only &s;ings</L>
<L>(As * and H**y preach) for queens and kings,</L>
<L>The nymph, that ne'er read Milton's mighty line,</L>
