<HEAD>IMITATIONS.</HEAD>
<P ID="CN026683.EP3V182"><PB N="57" REF="57">VER. 182. <HI>With &s;oups unbought,</HI>]
<Q><L>&mdash;dapibus men&s;as onerabat inemptis.</L> <BIBL>VIRG.</BIBL></Q></P>
